buildingOrderModule.simulator

Class TypeWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • buildingOrderModule.simulator.TypeWrapper

  • public class TypeWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    TypeWrapper.java --- Wrapper Class for all types (UnitType, UpgradeType, etc.) for the different Races in the game. This existence of this Class is necessary since the specified types do not have a shared super Class and therefore need to be combined due to the Simulator only working with a single type. The Simulator has to use a single class as wrapper for all its calculations.
    Author:
    P H - 12.07.2017
